eservation in Washington State.<\/p>\r\n<p>I got a lot out of the story, which is mainly about a 14-year-old boy who gets in trouble at his high school on the reservation and asks to transfer to an all-white school more than 20 miles away. That is something Sherman Alexie himself did, and he draws mostly from his own experiences. This makes the main character\u0027s cultural reality come to life in a really accessible and personal way.<\/p>\r\n<p>\r\nThe bittersweet honesty and simple factual storytelling earned my sincere respect. It\u0027s a brisk read and very worth picking up. The audiobook is read by the author and the print version contains a lot of illustrations by the author, so either way you are getting something more than just the story.\r\n<\/p>\r\n<p>\r\n<center>\r\n<a  href=\u0022http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/0316013692\/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=9325&creativeASIN=0316013692&linkCode=as2&tag=erfworld-20&linkId=AQVIKUTMRMDP6VLB\u0022><img border=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022http:\/\/ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/widgets\/q?_encoding=UTF8&ASIN=0316013692&Format=_SL110_&ID=AsinImage&MarketPlace=US&ServiceVersion=20070822&WS=1&tag=erfworld-20\u0022 ><\/a><img src=\u0022http:\/\/ir-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/e\/ir?t=erfworld-20&l=as2&o=1&a=0316013692\u0022 width=\u00221\u0022 height=\u00221\u0022 border=\u00220\u0022 alt=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\u0022 \/>\r\n<\/center>\r\n<\/p>\r\n<p>\r\n<a href=http:\/\/forums.erfworld.com\/viewtopic.php?f=19&t=7082>What book should Rob read next?<\/a>\r\n<\/p><\/div><a href=\u0022mod\/contactform\/index.php\u0022 class=\u0022ad_report_button\u0022>Report autoplaying audio or other bad ad.<\/a>","guid":44987}];
